Responsibilities:

  Maintenance of plants including pruning, watering and weeding
  Grass cutting 
  Removal of horticulture wastes
  Other ad-hoc duties as instructed by supervisor pertaining to landscape maintenance 

Requirements:

  WSQ Certified Landscape Technician preferred, otherwise must be willing to attend classes to obtain WSQ Certified Landscape Technician 
  Able to work outdoors under Singapore weather conditions
